  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Raising awareness on rainwater harvesting</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">12</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1	To raise awareness of rainwater harvesting at national and NGO level to enhance advocacy and lobbying to policy and decision makers
2	To strengthen the capacity of URWA and its members to effectively and efficiently promote rainwater harvesting in Uganda.
To promote research and development of appropriate technologies approaches and best practices in rainwater harvesting to inform learning decision making and project implementation</narrative>
