   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through joint action</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Uganda still has a lot to do in order to meet the MDG on water and sanitation. Rainwater harvesting is a viable option for the provision of clean water but has been greatly down played by the ministry of water and development actors. Uganda rainwater Association has been advocating for its promotion and RAIN foundation came in to support URWA in these activities.</narrative>
